data.description: This is a one of a kind!!! BRAND NEW FLOOR PLAN. Very reputable builder that has an eye for quality; you will not be disappointed! This very well thought out floorplan boasts a HUGE GARAGE!! All the upgrades you would find in a premier custom home without the huge price tag. Brighton Lakes is a gated community boasting amazing amenities including a fitness facility, a grand clubhouse and a large pool with lap lanes. SPLIT bedroom floor plan with a bonus room that can be used as a fourth bedroom or as an office or playroom. Downstairs features wood and tile floors and a beautiful kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy your covered patio perfect for entertaining or relaxing out back. Natural gas, tall ceilings, walk in shower, and a huge laundry room, are a few of the amazing quality features throughout. This deal won't last long!
